cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.MA

This paper deals with the optimization of data collection by a UAV over wireless sensor networks, which involves communication, navigation, and energy constraints. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization of the UAV's trajectory, which falls under the sub-category cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also formulates the problem as a dynamic programming problem, which falls under the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization of the sensors' transmit powers, which falls under the sub-category cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper involves numerical optimization, which falls under the sub-category cs.MA (Machine Learning).
